activation.en: Flip this card over when you activate this Skill.

effect.en: Once per Duel, during your Main Phase, if you have 5 or more DARK monsters in your GY with different names and control no monsters, you can banish 1 DARK monster from your GY then Special Summon 1 DARK monster from your GY.
